text: Ernst Beetschen (born 4 September 1953) is a Swiss skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1980 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Switzerland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1980 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
